      </ReturnValue>
      <Docs>
        <summary>
            Specifies whether OS Disk should be deleted or detached upon VMSS Flex
            deletion (This feature is available for VMSS with Flexible
            OrchestrationMode only). &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt; Possible values:
            &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt; **Delete** If this value is used, the OS disk is
            deleted when VMSS Flex VM is deleted.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt; **Detach**
            If this value is used, the OS disk is retained after VMSS Flex VM is
            deleted. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt; The default value is set to **Delete**.
            For an Ephemeral OS Disk, the default value is set to **Delete**. User
            cannot change the delete option for Ephemeral OS Disk.
            </summary>
